data.description: Welcome to your new home in the established neighborhood of Dark Forest Place, nestled on a spacious corner lot. This home offers an inviting front porch that enters into a spacious living room with a brick fireplace. Kitchen has tons of cabinets that leads into a formal dining room. Large Master on-suite with two additional  bedrooms and full bath. Nice sized back deck overlooks the backyard, which includes a quaint multipurpose workshop. The first room is more of a flex space and a door that leads to more of a workshop type area. New Roof and HVAC in 2022!
